@AtashaJordan Took me a while to figure out a routine, but my body finally agreed with:
- blackout curtains
- shower before bed
- aromatherapy herbal packs (I have a lavender eye mask & a hot/cold tea leave shoulder pad)
- a VERY cold bedroom
- white noise (fan or AC works for me)

@mei_newt It was Saturday--I was on news blackout from Wednesday morning around nine but at about 11 on Saturday random people at Eastgate started cheering and then the Audubon folks shouted the news across the street 😀.
